ext":"between the two affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fataxay~ara","text_ar":"فَتَخَيَّرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so he had the choice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"option, given him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-  See also 1. It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xay~ara bayona duwri AlA^anoSaAri","text_ar":"خَيَّرَ بَيْنَ دُورِ الاَنْصَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preferred some among the houses of the Assistants before others of them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And in another trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuy~ira","text_ar":"خُيِّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was preferred, and pronounced to have surpassed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcome,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"won,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a contest, or dispute. (IAth.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n11813","headword_ar":"خَيْرَةٌ","root":"xyr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayorN","text_ar":"خَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] used as an epithet: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayoraAtN","text_ar":"خَيْرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Akh, S, Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Also, used as a subst., or as an epithet in which the quality of a subst. is predominant,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good thing, of any kind: a good quality; an excellency:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a good act"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"action:"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: pl. as above:] see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayorN","text_ar":"خَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the former half of the paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11814","headword_ar":"خِيرَةٌ","root":"xyr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayorN","text_ar":"خَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places, towards the end of the paragraph: ―         -b2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyarapN","text_ar":"خِيَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places: ―         -b3-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaArN","text_ar":"خِيَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-  It is also a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAraA@ll~`hu","text_ar":"خَارَا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laka fiYh`*aAAlA^amori","text_ar":"لَكَ فِىهٰذَاالاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyarapN","text_ar":"خِيَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; both signifying [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blessing, prospering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of God; his"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causing one to have,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appointing to one, good in an affair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or his"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choosing for one the better thing in an affair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state that results to him who begs God to cause him to have good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to choose for him the better thing, in an affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna *`lika xiyrapF mina A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"كَانَ ذٰلِكَ خِيرَةً مِنَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That was through God's blessing, prospering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"through God's choosing the better thing in the affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)"}],"source_refs":["S"]},{"entry_id":"n11815","headword_ar":"خِيَرَةٌ","root":"xyr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyrapN","text_ar":"خِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(of which the former is the better known, TA) are substs. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotaArahu","text_ar":"اِخْتَارَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotaArahu A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"اِخْتَارَهُ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) both signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing, man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that one chooses:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chosen, selected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elected:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHam~adu xiyarapu","text_ar":"مُحَمَّدُ خِيَرَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hi mino xaloqihi","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهِ مِنْ خَلْقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyratuhu","text_ar":"خِيرَتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mohammad is the chosen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elect, of God, from his creatures"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Mgh: *) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyrapN","text_ar":"خِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAixotiyaArN","text_ar":"الاِخْتِيَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fidoyapN","text_ar":"فِدْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAifotidaA='u","text_ar":"الاِفْتِدَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyarapN","text_ar":"خِيَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaArN","text_ar":"خِيَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotiyaArN","text_ar":"اِخْتِيَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxay~arotu Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"تَخَيَّرْتُ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyrapN","text_ar":"خِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyarapN","text_ar":"خِيَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are syn.: (Msb:) see 8; and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaArN","text_ar":"خِيَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi xiyratiY","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ خِيرَتِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaratiY","text_ar":"خِيَرَتِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is what I choose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, (TA;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA xyrtY","text_ar":"هٰذَا خيرتى"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`w^ulaA='i xyrtY","text_ar":"هٰوُلَا=ءِ خيرتى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"These are what I choose."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxotaArN","text_ar":"مُخْتَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyrapN","text_ar":"خِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA","Mgh","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}